The case when error has type `AxiosError | Cancel`, when we call `axios.isCancel(err)`, the error value will change to type `never`

```typescript
function test(err: AxiosError | Cancel) {
  if (axios.isCancel(err)) {
    err // AxiosError | Cancel
  } else {
    err // never
  }
}
```
